Temporary Workaround

Both motors can be wired in parallel to M3 so they run together.

This means:

Motor A + and B + = connect to M3+
Motor A - and B - = connect to M3-
            
Both motors will then move together using the same control signal.

Limitations:
Robot can only move forward/back
Cannot turn

